entry.tran: （电子仪器发出的）哔哔声，嘟嘟声，短促尖锐的声音
entry.def: A bleep is a short, high-pitched sound, usually one of a series, that is made by an electrical device.

entry.tran: 发出哔哔声；发出嘟嘟声；发出短促尖锐的声音
entry.def: If something electronic bleeps, it makes a short, high-pitched sound.
